{"tid":611564,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"近排見到越黎越多人講 不反對 咁同贊成嘅分別係邊呢？","createTime":"2018-03-31T06:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T07:41:03.000Z","uid":59491,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07ff9f8227db5c07f9eec7226f90bed4515dbfd3","tid":611564,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:38:19.000Z","msg":"我嘅理解就咁<br />\n<br />\n不反對 = 唔會阻止人去贊成 但自己對件事冇咩立場 唔會身體力行去做 即係類似食花生咁<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 我唔反對啲人唔開冷氣 但我會開冷氣<br />\n<br />\n贊成= 我支持件事 我會願意去作出行動去支持 包括言語上反駁反對嘅人<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 我支持唔開冷氣 所以我會響應呢個行動"},{"pid":"e5af8cedfed1e413334dbd6d1a1896631a5d77de","tid":611564,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:44:42.000Z","msg":"我唔憎你係咪即係我愛你?"},{"pid":"4966b134def6769baa42c56182e417663cfcda0c","tid":611564,"uid":126283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:46:19.000Z","msg":"你自己咪答左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb67f7b61d40e3766abe62e925e4b68acdccbd66","tid":611564,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4966b134def6769baa42c56182e417663cfcda0c","tid":611564,"uid":126283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:46:19.000Z","msg":"你自己咪答左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:49:07.000Z","msg":"佢既理解係咁姐，但係其他人可以有自己既理解架嘛"},{"pid":"f4a7a928f7eeecc6ed35bedd634d25070d7737ec","tid":611564,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5af8cedfed1e413334dbd6d1a1896631a5d77de","tid":611564,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:44:42.000Z","msg":"我唔憎你係咪即係我愛你?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:53:26.000Z","msg":"簡單直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b80552843cc7519d4254f597f4f9915361d79bb","tid":611564,"uid":81270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"咁撚on9 都問得出"},{"pid":"f62c15187c1b5ae7627b036ad7795110297ea7bb","tid":611564,"uid":103936,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:21:49.000Z","msg":"用得雙重否定 都唔係老實人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩埋d語言藝術<br />\n<br />\n舉個例<br />\n我不反對同性戀 <br />\n<br />\n對住支持撚:我冇反對你地, 唔係同你地對立<br />\n對住反對撚:我冇支持過, 唔係同你地對立<br />\n對住中立撚:我已經表左態<br />\n<br />\n程度 : 支持&gt;不反對&gt;中立&gt;不支持&gt;反對<br />\n不反對 係一個比上不足比下有餘 嘅位置<br />\n1) 講 不反對 而唔講 不支持 暗示自己傾向支持<br />\n2) 講 不反對 而唔講 支持    暗示自己不支持 &gt; 傾向反對<br />\n想像下擲公字情景入面, 不反對係一個幾咁on9嘅位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f789a7c2c06c732344a1528f22bd20b295e7c8","tid":611564,"uid":45285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:41:03.000Z","msg":"咪就係二元論攪到連登咁低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有d小學雞用埋d垃圾論點黎鍵戰，就算我同小學雞都支持同一樣野，但唔代表我讚同小學論點。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}